          <h2 class="header--white">
           Our Alumni
          </h2>
         </div>
         <p class="p--intro">
          <p>
           Medill alumni represent the highest levels of accomplishment in journalism and marketing communications. By attending Medill, you join this network of powerful professionals working all over the world. This tight-knit group loves to help their fellow Medillians and Wildcats by serving as mentors and connections for future job opportunities.
          </p>
