   <div class="module">
    <section class="content-full">
     <div class="page">
      <div class="align-text-center">
       <div class="story__heading">
        Research Centers and Institutes
       </div>
       <h2 class="story__title">
        Innovation Through Application
       </h2>
       <p class="story__text">
        Medill is home to several research centers and institutes that produce cutting-edge research, develop new media products and greatly expand our knowledge of journalism and integrated marketing communications.
       </p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-two-col">
       <article class="feature-box zoom-image">
        <div class="feed feed__item--small">
         <div class="feed__card block__item--animate">
          <a class="feature__image" href="https://knightlab.northwestern.edu/">
           <img alt="Students in the Knight Lab work on a project on a computer" src="_images/homepage/900x600-boxes/Knight-Lab900x600.jpg"/>
          </a>
          <div class="feature__card__content container--gray-light feature-two-col__match-height">
           <h3 class="feature__card__heading">
            Knight Lab
           </h3>
           <div class="feed__item__content--text">
            <p>
             <p>
              <span>
               Knight Lab is a community of designers, developers, students and educators who work
               <span>
                on experiments designed to push journalism into new spaces. It's
                <span>
                 best known for its innovative suite of
                </span>
                open-source and
                <span>
                 adaptable
                </span>
                tools for media makers
                <span>
                 .
                </span>
               </span>
              </span>
             </p>
            </p>
           </div>
           <a class="button__link" href="https://knightlab.northwestern.edu/">
            Visit Knight Lab's website
           </a>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
       </article>
       <article class="feature-box zoom-image">
        <div class="feed feed__item--small">
         <div class="feed__card block__item--animate">
          <a class="feature__image" href="http://spiegel.medill.northwestern.edu/">
           <img alt="A person holds a mobile phone and icons show different types of media" src="_images/homepage/900x600-boxes/Spiegel-Research-Center900x600.jpg"/>
          </a>
          <div class="feature__card__content container--gray-light feature-two-col__match-height">
           <h3 class="feature__card__heading">
            Spiegel Research Center
           </h3>
           <div class="feed__item__content--text">
            <p>
             <p>
              <span>
               Spiegel Research Center conducts evidence-based, data-driven analyses to prove the relationship between customer engagement and purchase behavior.
              </span>
              <span class="s1">
               Its research has included proving the financial impact of consumer behavior in social media, mobile devices, customer reviews and more.
              </span>
             </p>
            </p>
           </div>
           <a class="button__link" href="http://spiegel.medill.northwestern.edu/">
            Visit Spiegel Research Center's website
           </a>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
       </article>
      </div>
     </div>
    </section>
   </div>
   <div class="module module--first">
    <section class="content-full">
     <div class="page">
      <div class="align-text-center">
